        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We frequently repair Samsung stove problems such as:</p>
            <ul>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Burner not igniting or heating</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Oven not reaching or maintaining temperature</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Uneven baking or roasting</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Stove shutting off unexpectedly</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Touch control panel not responding</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Error codes</strong> like SE, E-08, or C-21</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Broken or damaged glass cooktop</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Strange noises, odors, or electrical burning smell</strong></li>
