            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">We use only <strong>genuine Samsung parts</strong> to ensure optimal safety, performance, and longevity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="page-container" id="anchor-5">
        <div class="header-container">
          <div class="head-content-h">
            <h2>Should You Repair or Replace Your Samsung Stove?</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>We provide brand-specific recommendations based on your unit's condition:</p>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <li><strong>Repair</strong> – If your stove is under 12 years old, in good condition, and the repair cost is less than half the price of replacement</li>
              <li><strong>Replace</strong> – If it's older, has several major issues, or needs high-cost components like the glass cooktop and control board at the same time</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Typical Repair Costs</h3>
            <p>Your service fee includes:</p>

            <ul class="space-y-4">
